	* gtk-gui/CSharpBinding.CodeGenerationPanelWidget.cs,
	  gtk-gui/gui.stetic: Updated.

2007-01-29  Lluis Sanchez Gual <lluis@novell.com> 

	* Gui/CodeGenerationPanel.cs, CSharpBindingCompilerManager.cs,
